        public List<NotificationRegistrationKey> getStorageUnitNotificationRegistrationKeysByNotificationFilter(StorageUnitNotificationFilter businessObjectDataNotificationFilter)
        Description copied from interface: StorageUnitNotificationRegistrationDao
        Gets a list of keys for all existing storage unit notification registrations that match the specified storage unit notification filter parameters.
        Specified by:
        getStorageUnitNotificationRegistrationKeysByNotificationFilter in interface StorageUnitNotificationRegistrationDao
        Parameters:
        businessObjectDataNotificationFilter - the filter for the storage unit notification. Only the following four filter parameters are used to match the storage unit notification registrations:

        • the namespace of the business object definition (required, case-insensitive)
        • the name of the business object definition (required, case-insensitive)
        • the usage of the business object format (optional, case-insensitive)
        • the file type of the business object format (optional, case-insensitive)
        Returns:
        the list of storage unit notification registration keys
